title: Blackstone-Backed Liftoff Postpones IPO on Software Rout
description: Blackstone Inc.-backed Liftoff Mobile Inc. postponed its initial public offering, after tech stocks spiraled on concerns over the impact of artificial intelligence on operating companies.
